    "description": "Drishti Eye Care Holdings Services, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Radiologist for our Gwalior operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Drishti Eye Care Holdings Services:\nDrishti Eye Care Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Drishti Eye Care Holdings Services!",
